Interface Remote.IntSupplier

All Superinterfaces:
IntSupplier, Serializable
Enclosing class:
Remote
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public static interface Remote.IntSupplier extends IntSupplier, Serializable
Represents a supplier of int-valued results. This is the int-producing primitive specialization of Remote.Supplier.

There is no requirement that a distinct result be returned each time the supplier is invoked.

This is a functional interface whose functional method is IntSupplier.getAsInt().
